        public static long create(long requestId,
                          long adminId,
                          java.util.Date timeAccepted)
                   throws DaoException
        Creates a new agent using the data provided and caches it.
        Parameters:
        requestId - id of the request for which the agent is being created.
        adminId - id of the admin that is creating the agent.
        timeAccepted - the time of agent creation.
        Returns:
        the newly created agent's id or 0 if the agent could not be retrieved for caching after its creation.
        Throws:
        DaoException - if the agent could not be created or retrieved for caching.
